<plot>A carnal comedy version of High Fidelity set in a laundromat. Christine (jessica drake) is a beautiful woman who has just taken the plunge and finally kicked out her cheating boyfriend. Armed with a new sense of liberation now that she is single again, Christine sets out to live her life to the fullest. On one of her weekly trips to the laundromat, Christine runs into a handsome man named Scott (Brad Armstrong) who she immediately feels both an emotional and physical connection with. Scott is immediately attracted to Christine too and before long, the two find themselves in love. What Christine and Scott soon discover though is that when it comes to love it takes more than suds and fabric softener in common to keep a relationship afloat.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?198368</url></doc>
